.container
    .jumbotron.subhead
        %h1= @page_title = "Modules"
        %p.lead Game Settings
    %section
        .row
            = partial('modules_sidebar')
            .col-sm-9
                .page-header
                    %h1= @page_sub_title = "Potion Effects"
                :markdown
                    To give players potion effects use the `<potion>` module in a kit and apply it to players when they spawn or enter a region.
                    Potions effects will be applied directly to the player. Duration specifies how long the potion will last in seconds and amplifier what level / how strong the potion is. The potion type is specified using the [potion name](/reference/potion_effects).

                    To give a custom potion item to the player use the [items](/modules/items#potions) element and its `potions` attribute.

                %h5 Potion Element
                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Element
                                %th Description
                                %th Value
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<potion>')
                                %td
                                    The potion effects name.
                                %td
                                    %a{:href => "/reference/potion_effects"} Potion Name

                    %h5 Potion Attributes
                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Attribute
                                %th Description
                                %th Value
                                %th Default
                        %tbody
                            %tr{:title => "Required"}
                                %td
                                    %code duration
                                %td
                                    The time the potion effect last in seconds.
                                    %br
                                    %i Infinite duration can be specified by using <code>oo</code> as the duration.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary Number
                                    %span.label.label-danger Required
                                %td
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code amplifier
                                %td The strength of the potion effect.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary Number
                                %td 1
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code ambient
                                %td Specify if the potion's particle effects are ambient.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true/false
                                %td false

                :markdown
                        <potion duration="10" amplifier="4">damage resistance</potion>
                        <potion duration="900" amplifier="1" ambient="true">jump</potion>
